lead_paragraph: Before a mysterious job that arthitect Maggie Walsh has accepted in England begins, she and her boyfriend Pete go there for a vacation. Soon after they arrive in Britain, an accidental turn of events leads them to the estate of country gentleman for tea. They are surprised to learn that they were actually expected, along with several other guests. Before long the guests begin dying in violent ways, and to her horror, Maggie realizes that she was chosen for some kind of supernatural legacy by the owner of the estate.
